  ('dietitian-moex-04135', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'essay', '一位53歲男性汽修工人（焊接金屬／吸入橡膠），無家族肺癌病史，亦無抽菸、飲酒、嚼檳榔等習
慣。主訴：近3～5年體力下降，非計畫性體重減輕2～3 kg／2個月，聲音嘶啞約2個月（無喉嚨
痛）。經切片檢查後，診斷為肺癌（LLL／非小細胞／pT2aN1M0，stageⅡB）；因肺癌進行肺葉切除
術，進行LLL（左下肺葉）肺葉切除術／肺楔型切除術LUL（左上肺葉）／淋巴廓清術，並進行化學
治療及放射治療，周邊置入中心靜脈導管（PICC）。病人手術入院時的身高169.7公分，體重51.3公
斤，血清albumin：4.1 mg/dL、WBC：3,010×103/μL、hemoglobin：11.4 g/dL、PLT：11.4×103/
μL、creatinine：1.04 mg/dL、BUN：20 mg/dL。化療後病人食慾變差（自述為原有食量的一
半），進食後易有飽脹感，早上頭暈亦影響胃口，最近有看中醫用藥以增加食慾，目前可下床自由
活動。
請試述病人手術後接受化學治療及放射治療期間之熱量和蛋白質需求、完整營養診斷（PES；P為(1)
經口攝取不足 (2) BMI < 18.5 體重過輕）及飲食衛教重點。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": "3", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04136', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '營養照顧紀錄是醫療團隊成員之間溝通的工具，有關營養紀錄的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["營養介入內容要記錄在病歷中，但如果病人狀況良好飲食內容無調整可以不要記錄", "病歷中的營養紀錄要簡明扼要地總結營養照顧內容", "整個醫療團隊需要瞭解營養照顧之基本原則和方式，以提升照顧品質", "營養紀錄模式可以POMR、SOAP或ADIME等方式呈現"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04137', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關營養照護流程中營養評價（evaluation）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["病人每日熱量需要量為1,650大卡", "建議病人每天最多5份豆魚蛋肉類攝取", "病人過去偏愛水果，每次會吃一盤水果，一天吃兩次", "病人未依營養師飲食計畫增加蔬菜量攝取"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04138', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '營養照顧程序中，營養診斷之「PES」敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["P是problem", "E是evaluation", "S是signs", "S是symptoms"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04139', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '使用全靜脈營養輸液時，體重50公斤的病人，每日最大的葡萄糖供應量，下列範圍何者最適當？', '["50～140公克", "250～340公克", "350～440公克", "450～540公克"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04140', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '張先生83歲為腦中風患者，住院期間無法由口進食，則以鼻胃管提供營養，灌食結果消化情況尚 可，出院前評估張先生至少半年無法拔管進食，下列營養介入方式，何者最佳？', '["nasoduodenal（ND）feeding", "nasojejunal（NJ）feeding", "percutaneous endoscopic gastrostomy（PEG）feeding", "percutaneous endoscopic jejunostomy（PEJ）feeding"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04141', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關進行居家營養支持照顧的考慮因素，下列何者錯誤？', '["家庭環境衛生可以保護病人的健康和降低感染風險", "病人居家環境可提供充足的活動空間及設備", "能夠理解營養支持所需的相關技術、設備和用品的使用方式", "病人或家屬的財務和時間投入，可能導致的家庭經濟負擔"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04142', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '當病人考量停止靜脈營養前，經口攝入的營養素須持續可以滿足人體營養素需求的大約多少%？', '["30", "50", "75", "90"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04143', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關減重飲食控制的敘述，下列何者最不適當？', '["不論低脂、低醣或均衡的限制熱量飲食，長期都會產生類似的減重效果", "蛋白質攝取1.2公克／公斤體重，有助於降低lean body mass（LBM）的流失", "低醣飲食可能顯著增加血液尿酸濃度", "高脂低醣飲食通常含有較高的維生素B 、鈣及鎂 1"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b23ed10f357e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bf3ea9b1b4d4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
